# Configuración del Proyecto Certified

## Variables de Entorno

### NextAuth Configuration (REQUIRED)
NEXTAUTH_URL=http://localhost:3000
NEXTAUTH_SECRET=<generate with: openssl rand -base64 32>

### Keycloak Configuration (REQUIRED)
KEYCLOAK_CLIENT_ID=frontend-client
KEYCLOAK_CLIENT_SECRET=<obtain from Keycloak admin console>
KEYCLOAK_ISSUER=http://localhost:8080/realms/convalid

### Public Keycloak URL (for client-side redirects)
NEXT_PUBLIC_KEYCLOAK_ISSUER=http://localhost:8080/realms/convalid

### API Backend (REQUIRED)
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:8000

### Site Configuration
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=http://localhost:3000
NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_MEASUREMENT_ID=
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:8000

### Backend para rutas API de Next.js (servidor)
BACKEND_API_URL=http://localhost:8000

### Producción
# NEXTAUTH_URL=https://certified.example.com
# KEYCLOAK_ISSUER=https://keycloak.example.com/realms/convalid
# NEXT_PUBLIC_KEYCLOAK_ISSUER=https://keycloak.example.com/realms/convalid
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://api.example.com
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://certified.example.com
# NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_MEASUREMENT_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX

### Configuración de Email/Formularios (Opcional)
SMTP_HOST=smtp.example.com
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_USER=no-reply@certified.example.com
SMTP_PASS=your_smtp_password
CONTACT_EMAIL=info@certified.example.com

### reCAPTCHA (Recomendado para producción)
NEXT_PUBLIC_RECAPTCHA_SITE_KEY=your_recaptcha_site_key
RECAPTCHA_SECRET_KEY=your_recaptcha_secret_key

### Base de Datos (Si necesitas persistencia)
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@localhost:5432/certified

### Blockchain/API Keys (Para desarrollo)
BLOCKCHAIN_API_KEY=your_blockchain_api_key
IPFS_API_KEY=your_ipfs_api_key